1
00:00:51,479 --> 00:00:52,200
Master,

2
00:00:52,439 --> 00:00:53,679
where is the Demon King now?

3
00:00:53,880 --> 00:00:56,200
She's disguised as a dream-eating imp,

4
00:00:56,399 --> 00:00:59,479
hiding in the Netherworld Cave.

5
00:00:59,600 --> 00:01:00,560
Her name is

6
00:01:00,920 --> 00:01:01,840
Meng Li.

7
00:01:07,640 --> 00:01:08,599
Meng Li?

8
00:01:28,280 --> 00:01:29,719
She's young and innocent,

9
00:01:30,439 --> 00:01:31,879
unaware of her true nature.

10
00:01:32,640 --> 00:01:33,920
She's kind at heart

11
00:01:34,680 --> 00:01:36,400
and has never done anything truly evil.

12
00:01:37,519 --> 00:01:39,239
Please, Ancestral Master, have mercy on her.

13
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:55,599
By the law of karma,

14
00:01:55,799 --> 00:01:58,200
there are no pitiful people in this world.

15
00:01:58,560 --> 00:02:01,040
But with a compassionate heart,

16
00:02:01,400 --> 00:02:04,400
we see nothing but sorrow.

17
00:02:05,159 --> 00:02:08,040
There's only one way to save her.

18
00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:10,479
Please grant me the means to save her.

19
00:02:10,479 --> 00:02:13,080
With a strand of affection and a century of life,

20
00:02:13,080 --> 00:02:15,199
you can seal the Demon King's spiritual root,

21
00:02:15,199 --> 00:02:17,199
making him no different from a mortal.

22
00:02:17,400 --> 00:02:20,280
But if a mortal carries a demonic root,

23
00:02:20,280 --> 00:02:21,919
they will be backbitten.

24
00:02:22,560 --> 00:02:24,919
Not only will they lose their emotions,

25
00:02:24,919 --> 00:02:26,759
but also suffer shortened lifespans.

26
00:02:27,319 --> 00:02:29,199
Though it's a noble act,

27
00:02:29,560 --> 00:02:31,439
who would truly

28
00:02:31,439 --> 00:02:33,319
sacrifice themselves

29
00:02:33,639 --> 00:02:35,400
for the sake of the world?

30
00:02:35,479 --> 00:02:37,280
I'm not some savior,

31
00:02:40,080 --> 00:02:41,800
I just want to save my love.

32
00:02:42,319 --> 00:02:43,960
Have you thought it through?

33
00:02:43,960 --> 00:02:45,439
Sacrificing yourself

34
00:02:45,639 --> 00:02:46,919
to save the world

35
00:02:47,360 --> 00:02:49,280
is no easy task.

36
00:02:49,599 --> 00:02:50,680
I've made my decision.

37
00:03:07,680 --> 00:03:08,479
Daozhi.

38
00:03:09,039 --> 00:03:09,800
How did it go?

39
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:12,000
Did your master agree to our marriage?

40
00:03:14,159 --> 00:03:14,960
He did.

41
00:03:15,479 --> 00:03:16,120
Really?

42
00:03:16,639 --> 00:03:17,759
That's wonderful!

43
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:19,000
So soon,

44
00:03:19,479 --> 00:03:21,479
you'll be my husband?

45
00:03:21,759 --> 00:03:23,240
We'll be family.

46
00:03:23,439 --> 00:03:24,240
You're already

47
00:03:25,120 --> 00:03:27,280
more important to me than family.

48
00:03:28,879 --> 00:03:29,879
Don't worry.

49
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:31,319
From now on,

50
00:03:31,560 --> 00:03:33,479
I'll learn to live like mortals,

51
00:03:33,960 --> 00:03:35,039
and cherish every moment with you.

52
00:03:35,599 --> 00:03:36,560
No need to learn anything.

53
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:38,199
As long as we are together,

54
00:03:38,759 --> 00:03:39,759
that's all that matters.

55
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:43,479
Thank you, Dao.

56
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:44,800
In the past,

57
00:03:44,919 --> 00:03:46,800
I never understood

58
00:03:47,120 --> 00:03:49,680
why I was the only pixie without a clan.

59
00:03:50,199 --> 00:03:50,840
But now,

60
00:03:51,199 --> 00:03:52,360
I have you,

61
00:03:53,080 --> 00:03:54,479
Every day from now on,

62
00:03:55,159 --> 00:03:56,360
I'll have you by my side.

63
00:03:57,479 --> 00:03:58,879
From this moment,

64
00:03:59,199 --> 00:04:00,319
we'll grow old together,

65
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:03,919
and face life and death as one.

66
00:04:04,400 --> 00:04:05,400
Grow old together,

67
00:04:06,199 --> 00:04:07,360
face life and death as one.

68
00:04:54,279 --> 00:04:55,240
Dao's Will.

69
00:04:56,839 --> 00:04:58,040
Spiritual power of the sun.

70
00:04:58,920 --> 00:05:00,240
Make this vow a reality.

71
00:05:49,759 --> 00:05:50,680
A'Li.

72
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:57,199
In the next life,

73
00:05:59,560 --> 00:06:01,600
in the next life.

74
00:06:15,800 --> 00:06:16,600
A'Li!

75
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:25,160
No!

76
00:06:28,839 --> 00:06:29,439
No!

77
00:06:29,800 --> 00:06:30,879
No!

78
00:06:33,240 --> 00:06:34,480
No!

79
00:06:35,759 --> 00:06:37,040
No!

80
00:06:39,160 --> 00:06:40,439
No!

81
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:46,240
Daozhi!

82
00:06:50,160 --> 00:06:51,439
No!

83
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:53,759
Daozhi!

84
00:06:58,279 --> 00:06:59,560
The moon is lonely and bright.

85
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:01,279
Wind rises.

86
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:03,079
Apricots bloom.

87
00:07:04,160 --> 00:07:05,439
Memories

88
00:07:05,439 --> 00:07:06,519
like a dream.

89
00:07:07,920 --> 00:07:09,319
Tears fall.

90
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:07,039
I'm sorry

91
00:09:10,200 --> 00:09:11,960
for keeping you waiting.

92
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:13,240
A'Li.

93
00:09:25,399 --> 00:09:26,720
You remember

94
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:29,759
everything from a century ago?

95
00:09:32,480 --> 00:09:33,919
Pixies like A'Li

96
00:09:34,279 --> 00:09:36,000
taste best when raised.

97
00:09:36,559 --> 00:09:37,360
Li,

98
00:09:38,320 --> 00:09:39,440
I, Shen Daozhi,

99
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:40,600
swear to love you forever.

100
00:09:40,879 --> 00:09:41,679
If I ever break this oath,

101
00:09:42,399 --> 00:09:43,480
may I perish utterly.

102
00:09:43,799 --> 00:09:45,080
Tomorrow, I'll seek Master's blessing

103
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:46,320
for our marriage.

104
00:09:48,200 --> 00:09:49,720
It seems no matter how many lifetimes,

105
00:09:51,879 --> 00:09:53,279
I'll always fall for you.

106
00:10:47,600 --> 00:10:48,960
Let me help you with your hair.

107
00:11:17,759 --> 00:11:19,799
So this is your "never again"?

108
00:11:21,080 --> 00:11:22,799
I delved into the Underlying Dream,

109
00:11:23,200 --> 00:11:25,080
and found the truth.

110
00:11:25,559 --> 00:11:26,840
He had his reasons.

111
00:11:27,759 --> 00:11:29,600
Now that we're here,

112
00:11:29,759 --> 00:11:31,240
why not take back your Spiritual Root?

113
00:11:31,320 --> 00:11:32,720
I don't care

114
00:11:32,720 --> 00:11:33,600
what happened between you two.

115
00:11:33,600 --> 00:11:35,000
Shen Daozhi is dead.

116
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:37,000
The man standing before you is Shen Que.

117
00:11:37,200 --> 00:11:38,159
He colluded with Qingdu Temple

118
00:11:38,159 --> 00:11:39,720
and killed many of our kind.

119
00:11:40,039 --> 00:11:40,919
Showing mercy to him

120
00:11:40,919 --> 00:11:42,519
is a betrayal of our clan.

121
00:11:51,200 --> 00:11:51,919
This is...

122
00:11:52,039 --> 00:11:52,559
Yes.

123
00:11:53,039 --> 00:11:54,200
While you're catching up,

124
00:11:54,360 --> 00:11:56,799
the demon hunters have slaughtered our clan outside.

125
00:11:57,159 --> 00:11:59,039
Now their power has surged,

126
00:11:59,360 --> 00:12:01,919
they could wipe us out in a blink.

127
00:12:02,799 --> 00:12:04,200
The hunters' power has grown?

128
00:12:05,399 --> 00:12:06,759
There's something fishy.

129
00:12:07,080 --> 00:12:08,080
Then why not ask

130
00:12:08,080 --> 00:12:09,759
the Prince Xian beside you?

131
00:12:10,120 --> 00:12:11,840
He played a part in it.

132
00:12:29,960 --> 00:12:31,200
The village's location is exposed.

133
00:12:31,840 --> 00:12:33,240
Demon hunters will come again.

134
00:12:34,200 --> 00:12:35,320
If you hesitate,

135
00:12:35,879 --> 00:12:37,039
the Demon Clan will be wiped out,

136
00:12:37,039 --> 00:12:38,080
and that will be our fate too.

137
00:12:40,200 --> 00:12:40,879
A'Li,

138
00:12:41,440 --> 00:12:43,240
don't do anything you'll regret.
